WEBVTT

00:00:05.806 --> 00:00:08.141 line:90%
[♪ pop music playing]

00:00:50.058 --> 00:00:53.770 line:90%
PERFECT CROWN

00:01:04.656 --> 00:01:05.782 line:90%
THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION

00:01:05.866 --> 00:01:07.784 line:90%
CHILD ACTORS AND ANIMALS
WERE FILMED SAFELY

00:01:08.743 --> 00:01:09.744 line:90%
Tell me.

00:01:10.370 --> 00:01:12.038 line:90%
Who are you trying to save here? Yourself?

00:01:12.122 --> 00:01:13.206 line:90%
Or the Grand Prince?

00:01:15.959 --> 00:01:16.960 line:90%
Him.

00:01:17.836 --> 00:01:18.920 line:90%
[♪ tender music plays]

00:01:19.004 --> 00:01:20.881 line:90%
I can save myself.

00:01:22.173 --> 00:01:23.174 line:90%
You…

00:01:24.175 --> 00:01:25.468 line:90%
Please, Father.

00:01:30.682 --> 00:01:31.808 line:90%
[sighs]

00:01:37.564 --> 00:01:38.857 line:90%
Divorce him.

00:01:41.234 --> 00:01:44.237 line:90%
You bear the brunt of the allegations,
from ambitions for the throne

00:01:44.321 --> 00:01:46.364 line:90%
to the staged marriage,

00:01:46.990 --> 00:01:48.158 line:90%
and divorce him.

00:01:50.535 --> 00:01:51.536 line:90%
Father…

00:01:51.620 --> 00:01:53.455 line:90%
When he loses you, his weakness,

00:01:53.538 --> 00:01:55.707 line:90%
the opposition will
have nothing left to target.

00:01:55.790 --> 00:01:56.791 line:90%
Then the Grand Prince

00:01:57.876 --> 00:02:00.253 line:90%
will be able to fight back
without restraint.

00:02:12.766 --> 00:02:13.767 line:90%
[sniffles]

00:02:13.850 --> 00:02:14.851 line:90%
What if…

00:02:17.812 --> 00:02:19.689 line:90%
What if I want to save myself?

00:02:20.190 --> 00:02:21.816 line:90%
You said to choose between us.

00:02:23.860 --> 00:02:24.986 line:90%
That path, too,

00:02:26.112 --> 00:02:27.113 line:90%
leads to divorce.

00:02:32.786 --> 00:02:34.746 line:90%
Get out of that hellhole.

00:02:36.039 --> 00:02:37.499 line:90%
Avoid getting hurt any further.

00:02:49.511 --> 00:02:50.595 line:90%
[cries]

00:03:08.488 --> 00:03:12.409 line:90%
PERFECT CROWN

00:03:12.951 --> 00:03:14.619 line:20%
EPISODE 10

00:03:19.249 --> 00:03:21.710 line:20%
His Royal Highness is inside.

00:03:26.756 --> 00:03:28.216 line:20%
[breathes shakily]

00:03:32.345 --> 00:03:34.139 line:20%
-[door opens]
-[footsteps approaching]

00:03:46.693 --> 00:03:47.694 line:90%
Your Royal Highness.

00:03:51.114 --> 00:03:52.157 line:90%
[chuckles]

00:03:56.619 --> 00:03:58.038 line:90%
How's your father doing?

00:04:04.377 --> 00:04:07.714 line:90%
[chuckles] What's this? A gift?

00:04:11.176 --> 00:04:12.343 line:90%
[inhales sharply]

00:04:12.427 --> 00:04:14.137 line:90%
[sighs] Your Royal Highness.

00:04:16.056 --> 00:04:17.140 line:90%
Yes?

00:04:28.276 --> 00:04:29.444 line:90%
Let's get a divorce.

00:04:40.121 --> 00:04:43.833 line:90%
[sad music playing]

00:04:53.343 --> 00:04:54.427 line:90%
What are you talking about?

00:04:55.470 --> 00:04:56.471 line:90%
I think it's time…

00:05:01.309 --> 00:05:02.393 line:90%
we go our separate ways.

00:05:17.158 --> 00:05:18.409 line:90%
[sighs]

00:05:22.247 --> 00:05:23.915 line:90%
Father has fallen ill from all the stress.

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:28.962 line:90%
The stocks are tanking,
and public sentiment is in the mud.

00:05:33.633 --> 00:05:35.385 line:90%
I heard there's a tax audit coming soon.

00:05:36.344 --> 00:05:37.929 line:90%
No wonder he's fallen ill.

00:05:43.226 --> 00:05:45.436 line:90%
I got married to become the successor.

00:05:47.188 --> 00:05:48.189 line:90%
But at this rate,

00:05:49.816 --> 00:05:51.651 line:90%
I won't even have a place to go back to.

00:05:58.074 --> 00:05:59.534 line:90%
I hear what you're saying, but…

00:05:59.617 --> 00:06:00.660 line:90%
It's not your fault.

00:06:02.704 --> 00:06:04.164 line:90%
We were both in the wrong.

00:06:12.130 --> 00:06:13.131 line:90%
But now,

00:06:15.216 --> 00:06:16.801 line:90%
I want to cut my losses.

00:06:23.850 --> 00:06:25.059 line:90%
That's why you want a divorce?

00:06:26.394 --> 00:06:27.729 line:90%
To cut your losses?

00:06:27.812 --> 00:06:31.191 line:90%
The quickest fix for stuff like this
is someone stepping up to take the fall.

00:06:33.067 --> 00:06:34.736 line:90%
Holding out isn't always the answer.

00:06:41.034 --> 00:06:42.577 line:90%
Did something happen while I was gone?

00:06:43.369 --> 00:06:44.370 line:90%
Did the Queen Mother--

00:06:44.454 --> 00:06:47.832 line:90%
Whatever the Queen Mother says to me
is none of your concern.

00:06:49.918 --> 00:06:51.628 line:90%
-Seong Huiju.
-I already told you.

00:06:51.711 --> 00:06:52.921 line:90%
[♪ sad music continues]

00:06:53.004 --> 00:06:55.340 line:90%
I'm not afraid of that
because I had no honor to begin with.

00:06:56.883 --> 00:06:58.760 line:90%
Royal dignity, propriety, or whatever.

00:07:00.011 --> 00:07:01.888 line:90%
I couldn't care less
about any of that crap.

00:07:03.765 --> 00:07:05.516 line:90%
Does it even exist?

00:07:06.643 --> 00:07:08.603 line:90%
-Seong Huiju!
-Everything I have

00:07:10.313 --> 00:07:11.898 line:90%
actually has substance.

00:07:12.941 --> 00:07:14.901 line:90%
They're things I've fought for…

00:07:16.110 --> 00:07:17.820 line:90%
and claimed with my own hands.

00:07:24.577 --> 00:07:26.537 line:90%
You said the duty
of a royal is to be loved.

00:07:27.872 --> 00:07:29.165 line:90%
You said that was power.

00:07:32.460 --> 00:07:33.878 line:90%
But you lost it all.

00:07:36.589 --> 00:07:38.258 line:90%
What could you possibly do for me now?

00:07:51.104 --> 00:07:52.105 line:90%
Don't do this.

00:08:01.990 --> 00:08:03.992 line:90%
Not you too…

00:08:04.075 --> 00:08:05.576 line:90%
You said you wouldn't hold me back.

00:08:08.538 --> 00:08:10.206 line:90%
You told me to just keep taking.

00:08:13.209 --> 00:08:15.003 line:90%
But I'm just losing everything right now.

00:08:18.172 --> 00:08:19.173 line:90%
And yet…

00:08:21.634 --> 00:08:23.094 line:90%
you wish to keep me bound to you?

00:09:04.969 --> 00:09:07.972 line:90%
[♪ music ends]

00:09:26.908 --> 00:09:27.909 line:90%
Your Royal Highness.

00:09:27.992 --> 00:09:30.745 line:90%
This is the Crown Prince's Quarters.

00:09:33.623 --> 00:09:35.124 line:90%
It is a hall without a master.

00:09:35.958 --> 00:09:36.959 line:90%
Your Royal Highness.

00:09:37.043 --> 00:09:38.336 line:90%
I wish to be alone.

00:09:39.962 --> 00:09:41.381 line:90%
Go back to Anhwadang Hall.

00:10:08.908 --> 00:10:11.285 line:90%
[♪ gentle music plays]

00:10:28.970 --> 00:10:30.388 line:90%
[exhales shakily]

00:11:09.177 --> 00:11:10.428 line:90%
[cries]

00:11:52.261 --> 00:11:53.262 line:90%
[I-AN] <i>Brother.</i>

00:11:54.847 --> 00:11:56.307 line:90%
Look after the Crown Princess.

00:11:59.060 --> 00:12:00.645 line:90%
You are all she has to rely on.

00:12:01.771 --> 00:12:03.314 line:90%
Must you make things hard for her?

00:12:03.397 --> 00:12:04.398 line:90%
[scoffs]

00:12:05.983 --> 00:12:07.527 line:90%
She relies on me?

00:12:10.905 --> 00:12:12.657 line:90%
[sighs] Brother.

00:12:12.740 --> 00:12:15.952 line:90%
I doubt she ever relied on me.

00:12:16.994 --> 00:12:18.246 line:90%
But even if she did,

00:12:19.580 --> 00:12:21.958 line:90%
what could I possibly do for her?

00:12:27.547 --> 00:12:29.131 line:90%
I am sure she is well aware.

00:12:31.425 --> 00:12:32.635 line:90%
Such is the nature

00:12:33.844 --> 00:12:35.054 line:90%
of my station.

00:12:35.137 --> 00:12:37.098 line:90%
[♪ gentle music plays]

00:12:37.181 --> 00:12:39.850 line:90%
And the same must be said
for the Crown Princess.

00:12:45.773 --> 00:12:47.525 line:90%
You are just being a coward.

00:12:54.365 --> 00:12:55.366 line:90%
Sure.

00:12:59.078 --> 00:13:00.454 line:90%
I hope you do not end up like me.

00:13:04.750 --> 00:13:05.751 line:90%
No.

00:13:06.711 --> 00:13:07.795 line:90%
I don't intend to.

00:13:22.685 --> 00:13:23.978 line:90%
Is this how it felt?

00:13:24.979 --> 00:13:27.356 line:90%
[♪ music continues]

00:14:17.657 --> 00:14:19.158 line:90%
Did you work through the night?

00:14:28.125 --> 00:14:29.126 line:90%
Yeah.

00:14:39.136 --> 00:14:40.137 line:90%
What is it?

00:14:40.846 --> 00:14:41.847 line:90%
What?

00:14:42.431 --> 00:14:43.683 line:90%
Say what you need to say.

00:14:49.855 --> 00:14:51.732 line:90%
Please let me get into the Council Hall.

00:14:54.819 --> 00:14:56.612 line:90%
We need their approval for a divorce.

00:14:58.489 --> 00:14:59.824 line:90%
I'd like to speak for myself.

00:15:08.124 --> 00:15:09.125 line:90%
Do so, then.

00:15:19.176 --> 00:15:20.177 line:90%
Aide Choi.

00:15:21.679 --> 00:15:23.305 line:90%
Are they really going to get divorced?

00:15:24.306 --> 00:15:26.350 line:90%
[stammers] Well, what can we do?

00:15:26.434 --> 00:15:28.269 line:90%
The party involved is intent on it.

00:15:28.352 --> 00:15:30.438 line:90%
And the Grand Prince doesn't get a say?

00:15:31.021 --> 00:15:34.358 line:90%
Well, His Royal Highness agreed to it…

00:15:34.442 --> 00:15:37.236 line:90%
No, but you know he doesn't mean it!

00:15:37.319 --> 00:15:39.029 line:90%
What sort of nonsense is that?

00:15:42.241 --> 00:15:43.451 line:90%
Something happened yesterday.

00:15:46.620 --> 00:15:47.788 line:90%
Is the chairman making her?

00:15:52.084 --> 00:15:54.295 line:90%
Your Royal Highness.
By chance, did the chairman--

00:15:54.378 --> 00:15:55.379 line:90%
I'm getting a divorce.

00:15:56.046 --> 00:15:57.047 line:90%
Pardon?

00:15:57.131 --> 00:15:58.257 line:90%
The whole world

00:15:59.550 --> 00:16:01.719 line:90%
refers to me as a stain on his reputation.

00:16:03.179 --> 00:16:05.848 line:90%
-Your Royal Highness, that's just--
-Stain or weakness…

00:16:07.516 --> 00:16:09.560 line:90%
They should be eliminated regardless.

00:16:14.440 --> 00:16:16.108 line:90%
If His Royal Highness refuses…

00:16:20.613 --> 00:16:21.822 line:90%
I need you to take my side.

00:16:25.159 --> 00:16:26.952 line:90%
The chairman is just a bit frustrated.

00:16:27.036 --> 00:16:30.122 line:90%
He didn't put her up to anything.
[chuckles]

00:16:30.206 --> 00:16:32.583 line:90%
Then why? Why, all of a sudden?

00:16:32.666 --> 00:16:35.169 line:90%
[phone buzzing]

00:16:37.296 --> 00:16:38.631 line:90%
Don't go anywhere. Wait here.

00:16:41.967 --> 00:16:43.302 line:90%
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

00:16:45.012 --> 00:16:46.472 line:90%
[sighs]

00:16:53.771 --> 00:16:55.231 line:90%
I understand, Your Royal Highness.

00:16:58.359 --> 00:17:00.236 line:90%
[♪ tense music playing]

00:17:08.619 --> 00:17:10.120 line:90%
[court staff]
Announcing Grand Prince I-AN.

00:17:22.800 --> 00:17:24.510 line:20%
LORD INPYEONG

00:17:24.593 --> 00:17:25.594 line:90%
Two days ago,

00:17:26.887 --> 00:17:27.972 line:90%
the Cabinet requested

00:17:28.055 --> 00:17:31.517 line:90%
that His Royal Highness
cease his official duties…

00:17:35.771 --> 00:17:37.064 line:90%
His Royal Highness and I…

00:17:39.275 --> 00:17:40.568 line:90%
will be getting a divorce.

00:17:41.610 --> 00:17:42.778 line:90%
[staff chattering]

00:17:42.862 --> 00:17:44.738 line:90%
-What is this now?
-All of a sudden?

00:17:44.822 --> 00:17:45.823 line:90%
Grand Princess!

00:17:47.157 --> 00:17:48.450 line:90%
Strip me of my rank.

00:17:50.327 --> 00:17:52.705 line:90%
I risked it all to gain royal status,

00:17:52.788 --> 00:17:54.957 line:90%
was a prime suspect
in the Junghwajeon Hall fire,

00:17:55.666 --> 00:17:57.626 line:90%
and collapsed after being poisoned.

00:17:58.127 --> 00:17:59.461 line:90%
[scoffs]

00:17:59.545 --> 00:18:00.671 line:90%
That was all me.

00:18:01.171 --> 00:18:02.172 line:90%
Grand Princess.

00:18:02.256 --> 00:18:04.466 line:90%
My point is, do not pin this
on the wrong person.

00:18:05.885 --> 00:18:09.805 line:90%
It appears you do not grasp
the gravity of this situation.

00:18:09.889 --> 00:18:10.890 line:90%
[Huiju] Prime Minister Min.

00:18:13.642 --> 00:18:16.353 line:90%
I was told the royal family
are not subject to investigation.

00:18:17.605 --> 00:18:20.149 line:90%
Without the king's approval,
it is difficult, but…

00:18:20.232 --> 00:18:21.525 line:90%
If I am stripped of my rank,

00:18:22.318 --> 00:18:24.153 line:90%
it should be easier to investigate me, no?

00:18:28.908 --> 00:18:31.118 line:90%
Approve our divorce

00:18:32.912 --> 00:18:34.288 line:90%
and investigate me.

00:18:34.371 --> 00:18:36.707 line:90%
[♪ dramatic music plays]

00:18:36.790 --> 00:18:37.791 line:90%
Seong Huiju.

00:18:38.500 --> 00:18:41.003 line:90%
Whether I'm the culprit behind the fire,

00:18:41.086 --> 00:18:43.839 line:90%
or I staged my own collapse.

00:18:43.923 --> 00:18:47.927 line:90%
Either way, I can prove that
the Grand Prince had no part in any of it.

00:18:50.512 --> 00:18:51.513 line:90%
So just do it.

00:18:52.431 --> 00:18:55.434 line:90%
And all this insolent talk of him
relinquishing the regency…

00:18:57.144 --> 00:18:58.270 line:90%
Enough of that.

00:19:10.866 --> 00:19:12.785 line:90%
[reporters chattering]

00:19:13.827 --> 00:19:15.079 line:90%
[Taeju] Why are there so many?

00:19:15.663 --> 00:19:17.206 line:90%
Babe, you got this, right?

00:19:17.706 --> 00:19:19.416 line:90%
A walk in the park. [sniffles]

00:19:20.417 --> 00:19:21.919 line:90%
Why couldn't she just do it herself?

00:19:22.002 --> 00:19:24.088 line:90%
Huiju is the Grand Princess now.
How could she?

00:19:24.171 --> 00:19:26.131 line:90%
Besides, the camera loves you more.

00:19:27.299 --> 00:19:28.926 line:90%
That's true. [clears throat]

00:19:29.635 --> 00:19:30.636 line:90%
Let's go.

00:19:31.553 --> 00:19:32.554 line:90%
[clears throat]

00:19:33.973 --> 00:19:35.182 line:90%
[reporter] There's CEO Seong Taeju!

00:19:35.265 --> 00:19:36.350 line:90%
[reporters clamoring]

00:19:36.433 --> 00:19:37.893 line:90%
-CEO Seong!
-CEO Seong!

00:19:37.977 --> 00:19:39.061 line:90%
[shutters clicking]

00:19:39.144 --> 00:19:40.771 line:90%
-Please look over here.
-CEO Seong!

00:19:40.854 --> 00:19:43.691 line:90%
-CEO Seong!
-Over here, sir!

00:19:43.774 --> 00:19:45.818 line:90%
-Over here, please!
-CEO Seong!

00:19:45.901 --> 00:19:49.446 line:90%
ADDRESSING THE MARRIAGE CONTRACT LEAK

00:19:51.073 --> 00:19:52.324 line:90%
[clears throat]

00:19:54.535 --> 00:19:55.536 line:90%
Oh, right.

00:20:00.249 --> 00:20:02.668 line:90%
Can you confirm that Castle Group
had no knowledge

00:20:02.751 --> 00:20:05.421 line:90%
of the marriage contract
between the Grand Prince and Princess?

00:20:05.504 --> 00:20:08.882 line:90%
There must be some sort of plan
behind the three-year-divorce promise…

00:20:08.966 --> 00:20:11.343 line:90%
Following the marriage, has the handover
of her management rights

00:20:11.427 --> 00:20:13.512 line:90%
-been properly finalized?
-Just a moment.

00:20:13.595 --> 00:20:15.639 line:90%
First, let's calm down.

00:20:15.723 --> 00:20:18.851 line:90%
There are allegations that she staged
her collapse. Is that true?

00:20:18.934 --> 00:20:20.394 line:90%
[shutters continue clicking]

00:20:20.477 --> 00:20:22.271 line:90%
-What?
-To hide the fact it was staged,

00:20:22.354 --> 00:20:25.024 line:90%
she was taken to Castle Hospital
and not Royal Seoul Hospital.

00:20:25.107 --> 00:20:27.067 line:90%
-Is that true?
-[scoffs]

00:20:28.610 --> 00:20:30.654 line:90%
They're even calling that a lie now?

00:20:31.739 --> 00:20:32.740 line:90%
[clears throat]

00:20:34.825 --> 00:20:37.077 line:90%
[reporters clamoring]

00:20:39.621 --> 00:20:40.622 line:90%
Ma'am.

00:20:41.665 --> 00:20:44.209 line:90%
Why would she take poison
when she had the world at her feet?

00:20:45.085 --> 00:20:46.754 line:90%
[reporters clamor]

00:20:46.837 --> 00:20:49.381 line:90%
[♪ dramatic music playing]

00:20:53.093 --> 00:20:54.595 line:90%
<i>We just got started here.</i>

00:20:54.678 --> 00:20:56.638 line:90%
AIDE CHOI HYEON

00:21:01.602 --> 00:21:03.353 line:90%
Regarding the contract,

00:21:03.437 --> 00:21:06.690 line:90%
Castle Group will be
watering things down on our end.

00:21:06.774 --> 00:21:08.525 line:90%
So I'd appreciate your patience.

00:21:08.609 --> 00:21:11.195 line:90%
It won't be a perfectly clean slate,

00:21:11.779 --> 00:21:13.822 line:90%
but it'll lose enough steam
to make it manageable.

00:21:13.906 --> 00:21:16.533 line:90%
Do you truly believe
it is that simple a matter?

00:21:16.617 --> 00:21:18.869 line:90%
I'm sure you all know how much money

00:21:20.370 --> 00:21:21.538 line:90%
was poured into our wedding.

00:21:22.456 --> 00:21:25.667 line:90%
And that more was made
than was ever spent.

00:21:27.961 --> 00:21:29.338 line:90%
It's surely not news to you.

00:21:31.090 --> 00:21:33.592 line:90%
Before all contributors start asking
for their money back,

00:21:34.468 --> 00:21:37.179 line:90%
shouldn't we at least deny the fact
that this marriage

00:21:37.930 --> 00:21:39.431 line:90%
was a sham?

00:21:40.682 --> 00:21:41.767 line:90%
[Taeju] <i>For starters,</i>

00:21:41.850 --> 00:21:45.020 line:90%
I assume all of you have seen
this marriage contract.

00:21:45.813 --> 00:21:48.524 line:90%
Does the Grand Prince benefit
at all from this contract?

00:21:48.607 --> 00:21:49.900 line:90%
Same goes for my sister.

00:21:49.983 --> 00:21:52.736 line:90%
It stipulates that she'll relinquish
all assets and real estate

00:21:52.820 --> 00:21:55.155 line:90%
acquired with her royal title
upon divorce.

00:21:55.239 --> 00:21:56.615 line:90%
Did you all miss that part?

00:21:56.698 --> 00:21:59.535 line:90%
-But this was for status--
-Hold on. Let me just say one thing.

00:22:00.202 --> 00:22:02.955 line:90%
Everyone here knows
the palace was dead set against them

00:22:03.038 --> 00:22:06.375 line:90%
when the scandal
about them dating first broke.

00:22:06.458 --> 00:22:09.461 line:90%
Even our family didn't believe
they would actually get married.

00:22:09.545 --> 00:22:12.840 line:90%
We told her to stop wasting time
and just focus on her work.

00:22:12.923 --> 00:22:14.216 line:90%
But what could we do?

00:22:14.299 --> 00:22:15.676 line:90%
They were madly in love.

00:22:15.759 --> 00:22:18.011 line:90%
[reporters chattering]

00:22:18.095 --> 00:22:20.222 line:90%
[reporter 1]
Well, if they're so madly in love,

00:22:20.305 --> 00:22:22.516 line:90%
why would they agree
to divorce within three years?

00:22:23.058 --> 00:22:24.059 line:90%
Right.

00:22:24.852 --> 00:22:27.563 line:90%
That is why I'm here today.

00:22:28.814 --> 00:22:30.190 line:90%
That clause.

00:22:31.900 --> 00:22:33.861 line:90%
It was per my request.

00:22:33.944 --> 00:22:36.738 line:90%
[reporter 2] Does that mean you were
involved in drawing up the contract?

00:22:36.822 --> 00:22:38.448 line:90%
[reporter 3]
Between the Crown and Castle Group?

00:22:38.532 --> 00:22:41.785 line:90%
They may be madly in love now,
but feelings fade.

00:22:41.869 --> 00:22:44.371 line:90%
I mean, she was even drugged
at her own wedding.

00:22:44.454 --> 00:22:46.373 line:90%
-It could make her want a divorce.
-[reporters murmur]

00:22:46.456 --> 00:22:50.127 line:90%
But since divorce is considered taboo
in the royal family,

00:22:50.210 --> 00:22:53.297 line:90%
I suggested they at least
draw up a contract.

00:22:54.047 --> 00:22:55.382 line:90%
But let's be real.

00:22:55.465 --> 00:22:57.843 line:90%
This wasn't even notarized by a lawyer.

00:22:57.926 --> 00:23:00.721 line:90%
I just went a little overboard
to protect my little sister.

00:23:01.763 --> 00:23:05.058 line:90%
I sincerely apologize
for the distress caused to the public.

00:23:05.142 --> 00:23:06.351 line:90%
That said…

00:23:08.020 --> 00:23:11.481 line:90%
you all keep spinning these stories
about pulling stunts and plotting treason.

00:23:11.565 --> 00:23:13.150 line:90%
All sorts of ridiculous nonsense…

00:23:14.943 --> 00:23:17.112 line:90%
I'll be saving all your articles as PDFs.

00:23:17.196 --> 00:23:18.447 line:90%
[reporters clamor]

00:23:18.530 --> 00:23:19.615 line:90%
[clears throat]

00:23:22.993 --> 00:23:25.495 line:90%
[reporters clamor]

00:23:26.121 --> 00:23:27.789 line:90%
[♪ upbeat music plays]

00:23:27.873 --> 00:23:29.416 line:90%
You were so awesome, babe!

00:23:30.626 --> 00:23:32.127 line:90%
-Let's hurry home.
-Okay.

00:23:33.879 --> 00:23:35.672 line:20%
<i>…all your articles as PDFs.</i>

00:23:35.756 --> 00:23:37.966 line:90%
-You reviewed the draft for the PR team?
-Yes.

00:23:38.467 --> 00:23:41.845 line:90%
"Doting siblings," check.
"True love," check.

00:23:41.929 --> 00:23:43.513 line:90%
"Saving as PDFs," check.

00:23:44.264 --> 00:23:45.349 line:90%
All done.

00:23:45.432 --> 00:23:46.725 line:90%
Yes, I knew it!

00:23:46.808 --> 00:23:49.728 line:90%
They couldn't even look at each other
during the wedding rites

00:23:49.811 --> 00:23:51.813 line:90%
without blushing and getting all giddy.

00:23:51.897 --> 00:23:55.651 line:90%
How could that <i>not</i> be true love?

00:23:58.362 --> 00:23:59.738 line:90%
[sighs]

00:24:02.658 --> 00:24:03.742 line:90%
[sighs]

00:24:05.244 --> 00:24:06.620 line:90%
It should be over by now.

00:24:06.703 --> 00:24:09.456 line:90%
Without even consulting
with the Royal Secretariat?

00:24:09.539 --> 00:24:13.502 line:90%
We made it crystal clear that the Crown
has no ties to the contract.

00:24:14.086 --> 00:24:18.507 line:90%
We also clarified that the Grand Prince
stood to gain nothing from our marriage.

00:24:19.091 --> 00:24:20.801 line:90%
Any remaining controversy

00:24:21.468 --> 00:24:22.886 line:90%
will be mine to handle.

00:24:24.638 --> 00:24:26.139 line:90%
Once you cast me aside,

00:24:27.474 --> 00:24:29.101 line:90%
the Grand Prince can return…

00:24:31.520 --> 00:24:33.188 line:90%
to being the pride of the Crown.

00:24:34.022 --> 00:24:35.107 line:90%
[chuckles]

00:24:35.732 --> 00:24:37.526 line:90%
[officials murmuring]

00:24:39.069 --> 00:24:40.320 line:90%
Does His Royal Highness…

00:24:41.446 --> 00:24:43.156 line:90%
share this sentiment?

00:24:47.494 --> 00:24:49.246 line:90%
[♪ suspenseful music plays]

00:25:20.110 --> 00:25:21.653 line:90%
Grand Prince I-AN

00:25:21.737 --> 00:25:23.655 line:90%
shall receive His Majesty's command.

00:25:31.246 --> 00:25:32.581 line:90%
[♪ music ends]

00:25:35.625 --> 00:25:38.462 line:90%
[♪ gentle music plays]

00:26:01.568 --> 00:26:02.903 line:90%
Is this how it felt?

00:26:15.123 --> 00:26:18.377 line:90%
[♪ classical music plays]

00:26:26.968 --> 00:26:27.969 line:90%
Even so…

00:26:34.267 --> 00:26:35.977 line:90%
I refuse to live like you.

00:26:36.061 --> 00:26:38.105 line:90%
[♪ dramatic music plays]

00:27:16.184 --> 00:27:17.436 line:90%
Your Royal Highness.

00:27:17.519 --> 00:27:20.188 line:90%
His Majesty has just retired
to his bedchamber.

00:27:20.272 --> 00:27:21.731 line:90%
-Perhaps you can--
-Announce me.

00:27:23.024 --> 00:27:24.192 line:90%
Your Royal Highness.

00:27:26.153 --> 00:27:27.320 line:90%
I told you to announce me.

00:27:30.615 --> 00:27:31.783 line:90%
Your Majesty,

00:27:31.867 --> 00:27:33.785 line:90%
His Royal Highness has arrived.

00:27:35.912 --> 00:27:37.122 line:90%
[King] Show him in.

00:27:37.622 --> 00:27:39.624 line:90%
[♪ dramatic music continues]

00:27:59.102 --> 00:28:00.103 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:28:03.231 --> 00:28:04.357 line:90%
I must ask you

00:28:06.109 --> 00:28:07.694 line:90%
to return my throne.

00:28:14.201 --> 00:28:16.953 line:90%
"Thus proclaims the King."

00:28:18.330 --> 00:28:19.956 line:90%
-"I, the King…"
-[King Seonjong] <i>I, the King,</i>

00:28:20.040 --> 00:28:22.083 line:90%
<i>being overburdened in body and spirit,</i>

00:28:22.167 --> 00:28:24.461 line:90%
<i>can no longer govern the realm.</i>

00:28:26.379 --> 00:28:28.256 line:90%
<i>Thus, I intend to step down</i>
<i>from the throne.</i>

00:28:30.717 --> 00:28:33.845 line:90%
<i>The Crown Prince is far too young</i>

00:28:33.929 --> 00:28:35.597 line:90%
<i>and of a frail disposition</i>

00:28:36.223 --> 00:28:37.891 line:90%
<i>to assume such a heavy responsibility.</i>

00:28:38.934 --> 00:28:41.603 line:90%
<i>Fortunately, the heavens</i>
<i>have not forsaken us,</i>

00:28:42.312 --> 00:28:43.855 line:90%
<i>and have bestowed upon us the wise</i>

00:28:44.523 --> 00:28:45.941 line:90%
<i>and virtuous Grand Prince I-AN.</i>

00:28:46.566 --> 00:28:47.651 line:90%
"I deem him fit

00:28:48.151 --> 00:28:51.363 line:90%
to serve the heavens
and the royal ancestors above,

00:28:51.446 --> 00:28:54.950 line:90%
and to care for the people
of the realm below."

00:28:55.659 --> 00:28:57.452 line:90%
As such, I, the King,

00:28:57.536 --> 00:28:59.871 line:90%
intend to abdicate the throne
in favor of my uncle,

00:28:59.955 --> 00:29:01.748 line:90%
Grand Prince I-AN.

00:29:03.333 --> 00:29:06.127 line:90%
"All officials of the Crown
and the Cabinet

00:29:06.211 --> 00:29:09.172 line:90%
shall receive and uphold
the new King with might."

00:29:11.132 --> 00:29:14.302 line:90%
[King Seonjong] <i>And all the people shall</i>
<i>embrace the grand vision of the nation…</i>

00:29:14.386 --> 00:29:15.554 line:90%
"THIRTY-SECOND KING"

00:29:15.637 --> 00:29:17.305 line:90%
<i>…so that the realm may stand firm,</i>

00:29:18.098 --> 00:29:20.892 line:90%
<i>unshaken and everlasting.</i>

00:29:26.565 --> 00:29:28.775 line:90%
What is the meaning of this?

00:29:29.609 --> 00:29:31.236 line:90%
A willful abdication?

00:29:31.319 --> 00:29:32.946 line:90%
I must see His Majesty.

00:29:34.406 --> 00:29:35.407 line:90%
Lord INPYEONG.

00:29:36.408 --> 00:29:37.867 line:90%
Do you dismiss the royal command

00:29:40.453 --> 00:29:41.705 line:90%
delivered by the Royal Secretariat?

00:29:44.207 --> 00:29:46.459 line:90%
[♪ triumphant music plays]

00:30:04.352 --> 00:30:05.854 line:90%
[♪ music ends]

00:30:05.937 --> 00:30:07.063 line:90%
Your Royal Highness.

00:30:08.565 --> 00:30:09.899 line:90%
Just hold on a second.

00:30:22.245 --> 00:30:23.705 line:90%
You said you were done losing.

00:30:26.583 --> 00:30:27.917 line:90%
That's why you want a divorce.

00:30:29.127 --> 00:30:30.128 line:90%
[sighs]

00:30:30.795 --> 00:30:31.796 line:90%
Your Royal Highness.

00:30:32.422 --> 00:30:34.049 line:90%
-I just…
-And yet,

00:30:34.674 --> 00:30:36.551 line:90%
how could you throw
everything on the line?

00:30:40.055 --> 00:30:41.097 line:90%
Did you truly believe…

00:30:45.477 --> 00:30:46.478 line:90%
I could not…

00:30:50.607 --> 00:30:51.650 line:90%
protect us?

00:30:56.446 --> 00:30:57.447 line:90%
It's not that…

00:30:57.530 --> 00:30:58.865 line:90%
You did not trust me.

00:31:21.638 --> 00:31:22.972 line:90%
Willful abdication?

00:31:23.056 --> 00:31:27.602 line:90%
The royal edict was announced in front
of the Cabinet and the royal family.

00:31:29.437 --> 00:31:30.605 line:90%
Why, all of a sudden?

00:31:33.149 --> 00:31:34.567 line:90%
Without so much as a warning.

00:31:38.321 --> 00:31:40.490 line:90%
-Tell me why!
-Please calm down, Your Majesty.

00:31:42.867 --> 00:31:45.620 line:90%
Fortunately, His Royal Highness refused…

00:31:45.704 --> 00:31:47.539 line:90%
That was just a formality!

00:31:48.748 --> 00:31:50.417 line:90%
He will refuse three times…

00:31:52.669 --> 00:31:53.753 line:90%
before he accepts.

00:31:57.132 --> 00:31:59.551 line:90%
[scoffs, cries]

00:32:07.183 --> 00:32:09.561 line:90%
That feeble bloodline has at last…

00:32:14.899 --> 00:32:15.942 line:90%
[grunts]

00:32:18.820 --> 00:32:19.946 line:90%
[straining]

00:32:21.072 --> 00:32:22.240 line:90%
[sighs]

00:32:25.994 --> 00:32:26.995 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:32:27.078 --> 00:32:28.371 line:90%
Open the doors.

00:32:28.455 --> 00:32:31.666 line:90%
[court lady] His Majesty has locked them
from the inside.

00:32:31.750 --> 00:32:32.751 line:90%
[Yun] Your Majesty!

00:32:34.502 --> 00:32:35.920 line:90%
Open these doors!

00:32:36.796 --> 00:32:39.215 line:90%
-Your Majesty!
-[court lady] Please stop, Your Majesty.

00:32:39.299 --> 00:32:41.217 line:90%
[Yun] This is beyond the pale.

00:32:41.718 --> 00:32:42.719 line:90%
Your Majesty!

00:32:44.679 --> 00:32:47.348 line:90%
[Yun] <i>Have you truly gone mad?</i>

00:32:48.892 --> 00:32:50.268 line:90%
<i>I would rather see you dead.</i>

00:32:54.105 --> 00:32:55.106 line:90%
Your Majesty!

00:32:55.774 --> 00:32:58.151 line:90%
Your Majesty,
please give His Majesty some time.

00:32:58.234 --> 00:32:59.903 line:90%
What is this time you speak of?

00:33:00.904 --> 00:33:01.905 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:33:04.908 --> 00:33:06.576 line:90%
You must have known.

00:33:07.869 --> 00:33:09.454 line:90%
-Pardon?
-Court Lady Im.

00:33:09.537 --> 00:33:10.622 line:90%
[Im] Yes, Your Majesty.

00:33:10.705 --> 00:33:12.582 line:90%
[♪ tense music plays]

00:33:12.665 --> 00:33:13.917 line:90%
Break down these doors.

00:33:14.542 --> 00:33:15.543 line:90%
Your Majesty…

00:33:15.627 --> 00:33:17.086 line:90%
These are the King's Quarters.

00:33:17.796 --> 00:33:20.089 line:90%
How could I open them
without His Majesty's command?

00:33:23.092 --> 00:33:25.261 line:90%
Please rescind your command.

00:33:27.639 --> 00:33:29.641 line:90%
Start a fire if you must.

00:33:32.060 --> 00:33:33.603 line:90%
That should force him out.

00:33:42.278 --> 00:33:43.279 line:90%
[Jeongwoo] Your Majesty.

00:33:47.534 --> 00:33:49.077 line:90%
Let me escort you to your quarters.

00:33:50.620 --> 00:33:52.121 line:90%
Do not give me orders.

00:33:54.249 --> 00:33:55.250 line:90%
I have yet…

00:33:56.960 --> 00:33:58.044 line:90%
to give an order.

00:34:10.014 --> 00:34:11.224 line:90%
[♪ music ends]

00:34:12.350 --> 00:34:14.227 line:90%
We must allow no word of this to spread.

00:34:15.395 --> 00:34:17.188 line:90%
I will handle the Cabinet members.

00:34:17.272 --> 00:34:19.691 line:90%
You must see to it
that no word escapes the palace.

00:34:23.695 --> 00:34:25.947 line:90%
Am I the only one
horrified by this situation?

00:34:26.990 --> 00:34:28.283 line:90%
It is getting quite exhausting.

00:34:28.783 --> 00:34:31.744 line:90%
How much longer must I keep cleaning up
the royal family's mess?

00:34:36.374 --> 00:34:38.001 line:90%
This affects you as well.

00:34:42.130 --> 00:34:43.631 line:90%
If Grand Prince I-AN becomes king,

00:34:43.715 --> 00:34:45.884 line:90%
the Grand Princess will be bound
to the palace forever.

00:34:45.967 --> 00:34:47.051 line:90%
Is that what you desire?

00:34:49.137 --> 00:34:50.430 line:90%
That will not happen.

00:34:56.060 --> 00:34:58.479 line:90%
The Grand Prince will refuse three times
as a formality.

00:34:58.563 --> 00:35:02.150 line:90%
He refused once at the Council Hall today,
so he'll refuse two more times.

00:35:02.233 --> 00:35:03.234 line:90%
Before he does,

00:35:04.527 --> 00:35:07.155 line:90%
you must stop either
the Grand Prince or His Majesty.

00:35:09.532 --> 00:35:11.075 line:90%
Do whatever you must.

00:35:17.540 --> 00:35:19.459 line:90%
I shall put her poisoning case on hold.

00:35:20.209 --> 00:35:21.544 line:90%
But you agreed to handle that--

00:35:21.628 --> 00:35:23.504 line:90%
The handling of affairs you desire

00:35:23.588 --> 00:35:25.465 line:90%
shall be granted to you

00:35:27.091 --> 00:35:28.217 line:90%
once I get what I want.

00:35:33.723 --> 00:35:36.225 line:90%
Are you threatening me right now?

00:35:37.018 --> 00:35:38.019 line:90%
Yes.

00:35:39.604 --> 00:35:41.314 line:90%
Is there any reason I should not?

00:36:01.751 --> 00:36:02.835 line:90%
[sighs]

00:36:03.586 --> 00:36:05.046 line:90%
You did not trust me.

00:36:07.590 --> 00:36:08.758 line:90%
[sighs]

00:36:14.847 --> 00:36:16.140 line:90%
[footsteps approaching]

00:36:18.726 --> 00:36:20.937 line:90%
Why is it just you?
Where's the Grand Prince?

00:36:21.521 --> 00:36:22.605 line:90%
He left.

00:36:22.689 --> 00:36:25.191 line:90%
-He left? The palace?
-Yes.

00:36:26.234 --> 00:36:28.945 line:90%
What is he thinking,
leaving at a time like this?

00:36:29.737 --> 00:36:31.531 line:90%
He nearly died as just the Grand Prince.

00:36:31.614 --> 00:36:34.325 line:90%
Who knows what'll happen
after this royal abdication edict?

00:36:34.409 --> 00:36:35.410 line:90%
[dialing]

00:36:45.503 --> 00:36:46.504 line:90%
[phone ringing]

00:36:46.587 --> 00:36:47.839 line:90%
INCOMING CALL
JUNIOR ALUM

00:36:57.306 --> 00:36:58.933 line:90%
[line ringing]

00:36:59.976 --> 00:37:01.144 line:90%
[sighs]

00:37:01.644 --> 00:37:02.645 line:90%
Stop it.

00:37:05.857 --> 00:37:07.567 line:90%
How will you ever divorce him
at this rate?

00:37:14.824 --> 00:37:17.035 line:90%
Aide Choi and I will find
the Grand Prince.

00:37:17.827 --> 00:37:19.120 line:90%
You stay here.

00:37:19.203 --> 00:37:20.747 line:90%
Can't have you missing each other.

00:37:34.927 --> 00:37:35.928 line:90%
[sighs]

00:37:36.596 --> 00:37:38.514 line:90%
[♪ gentle music plays]

00:37:40.433 --> 00:37:41.642 line:90%
[sighs]

00:37:57.909 --> 00:37:59.702 line:90%
If I say I wish to ascend the throne,

00:38:00.912 --> 00:38:02.663 line:90%
all would condemn me and hurl insults.

00:38:06.501 --> 00:38:07.502 line:90%
But I believe

00:38:08.628 --> 00:38:09.796 line:90%
you would understand me.

00:38:09.879 --> 00:38:12.340 line:90%
[♪ contemplative music playing]

00:38:14.675 --> 00:38:15.760 line:90%
<i>"Leading the way."</i>

00:38:16.636 --> 00:38:17.637 line:90%
<i>How do you do it?</i>

00:38:20.681 --> 00:38:22.225 line:90%
You just need to walk by my side.

00:38:24.143 --> 00:38:25.269 line:90%
I'll teach you.

00:38:27.522 --> 00:38:29.524 line:90%
[♪ contemplative music continues]

00:38:42.662 --> 00:38:43.663 line:90%
[exhales deeply]

00:38:43.746 --> 00:38:45.748 line:90%
[♪ pop music playing, WOODZ "Everglow"]

00:38:55.341 --> 00:38:56.676 line:90%
Just let me be for a second.

00:38:57.343 --> 00:38:59.470 line:90%
I'll come back down
once my anger subsides a bit.

00:39:06.519 --> 00:39:07.728 line:90%
[I-AN clears throat]

00:39:26.414 --> 00:39:27.415 line:90%
[I-AN] <i>I do like you.</i>

00:39:29.041 --> 00:39:30.042 line:90%
<i>And it's my first time.</i>

00:39:31.043 --> 00:39:32.378 line:90%
You should just accept it all.

00:39:34.130 --> 00:39:35.756 line:90%
Whether it be money, honor,

00:39:37.550 --> 00:39:38.551 line:90%
or my heart…

00:39:45.850 --> 00:39:46.851 line:90%
[sniffles]

00:39:51.939 --> 00:39:52.940 line:90%
[sobs]

00:39:55.568 --> 00:39:56.569 line:90%
[sobbing]

00:40:30.269 --> 00:40:31.646 line:90%
[♪ music ends]

00:40:35.900 --> 00:40:37.818 line:90%
Aide Do, here's what you asked for.

00:40:38.361 --> 00:40:40.238 line:90%
-Let's go.
-Where?

00:40:40.321 --> 00:40:43.783 line:90%
His Royal Highness left the palace
and won't take the Grand Princess's calls.

00:40:43.866 --> 00:40:45.993 line:90%
What? What about the Royal Guard?

00:40:46.077 --> 00:40:48.371 line:90%
No need to call them. I know where he is.

00:40:48.454 --> 00:40:50.414 line:90%
[I-AN] <i>After the royal abdication edict</i>
<i>is delivered,</i>

00:40:50.498 --> 00:40:53.251 line:90%
<i>His Majesty will lock himself</i>
<i>in his quarters.</i>

00:40:53.918 --> 00:40:56.045 line:90%
<i>I will leave and head to</i>
<i>my private residence.</i>

00:40:56.712 --> 00:40:58.089 line:90%
<i>I must be gone</i>

00:40:58.756 --> 00:41:00.800 line:90%
<i>so the Grand Princess</i>
<i>does not get embroiled in the chaos.</i>

00:41:00.883 --> 00:41:01.884 line:90%
[sighs]

00:41:02.510 --> 00:41:04.011 line:90%
I understand, Your Royal Highness.

00:41:04.720 --> 00:41:06.973 line:90%
Wow, so you knew all along?

00:41:07.056 --> 00:41:08.849 line:90%
Then why didn't you loop me in?

00:41:09.767 --> 00:41:11.769 line:90%
You didn't loop me in, either.

00:41:11.852 --> 00:41:13.271 line:90%
About the Grand Princess's plan.

00:41:14.272 --> 00:41:15.481 line:90%
Right. That's true.

00:41:17.149 --> 00:41:18.776 line:90%
Wait, so where are we going?

00:41:18.859 --> 00:41:20.987 line:90%
-To get a drink.
-[Hyeon] What?

00:41:26.701 --> 00:41:28.494 line:90%
[breathing heavily]

00:41:29.287 --> 00:41:30.913 line:90%
[Hyejeong] Everything's a mess anyway.

00:41:30.997 --> 00:41:33.749 line:90%
Might as well have a drink
since it's not allowed in the palace.

00:41:33.833 --> 00:41:35.793 line:90%
Well, th-that's true…

00:41:35.876 --> 00:41:37.878 line:90%
[breathes deeply]

00:41:42.675 --> 00:41:43.676 line:90%
[Hyejeong sighs]

00:41:45.928 --> 00:41:46.929 line:90%
This is it.

00:41:47.638 --> 00:41:48.973 line:90%
This is what I like.

00:41:51.434 --> 00:41:52.435 line:90%
That's random.

00:41:56.272 --> 00:41:57.523 line:90%
You asked what I liked.

00:41:59.066 --> 00:42:00.109 line:90%
This is what I like.

00:42:01.277 --> 00:42:02.320 line:90%
With the Hangang River here.

00:42:05.031 --> 00:42:06.032 line:90%
[sighs]

00:42:06.115 --> 00:42:08.117 line:90%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:42:21.255 --> 00:42:22.256 line:90%
[sighs]

00:42:25.718 --> 00:42:26.927 line:90%
What do you think?

00:42:27.011 --> 00:42:28.012 line:90%
[smacks lips]

00:42:28.095 --> 00:42:29.096 line:90%
Well, it's…

00:42:30.514 --> 00:42:31.807 line:90%
I-I like it.

00:42:35.019 --> 00:42:36.145 line:90%
[chuckles softly]

00:42:37.271 --> 00:42:38.397 line:90%
What exactly?

00:42:39.690 --> 00:42:40.733 line:90%
The river?

00:42:42.151 --> 00:42:43.152 line:90%
The alcohol?

00:42:44.945 --> 00:42:45.946 line:90%
Or me?

00:42:47.823 --> 00:42:49.658 line:90%
[♪ hopeful music playing]

00:43:02.963 --> 00:43:04.256 line:90%
[inhales sharply]

00:43:08.302 --> 00:43:09.303 line:90%
[chuckles softly]

00:43:16.477 --> 00:43:17.478 line:90%
[chuckles]

00:43:27.405 --> 00:43:28.406 line:90%
[exhales sharply]

00:43:29.532 --> 00:43:30.533 line:90%
[breathes deeply]

00:43:33.119 --> 00:43:34.120 line:90%
[Hyeon mutters]

00:43:34.787 --> 00:43:37.706 line:90%
-I like it all. I like the whole lot.
-[chuckles]

00:43:37.790 --> 00:43:39.792 line:90%
[crickets chirping]

00:43:43.087 --> 00:43:44.255 line:90%
[Huiju] <i>Where are you?</i>

00:43:44.839 --> 00:43:46.382 line:90%
<i>Did you have dinner?</i>

00:43:46.465 --> 00:43:49.969 line:90%
<i>I get that you're angry and all,</i>
<i>but how could you just leave like this?</i>

00:43:50.052 --> 00:43:50.886 line:90%
[sighs]

00:43:50.970 --> 00:43:53.139 line:90%
<i>You're somewhere safe, right?</i> [sighs]

00:43:53.222 --> 00:43:55.307 line:90%
<i>I swear, I will track your location.</i>

00:43:56.934 --> 00:44:00.020 line:90%
Is Aide Do even looking for him or what?

00:44:02.398 --> 00:44:03.399 line:90%
Your Royal Highness.

00:44:04.984 --> 00:44:05.985 line:90%
Yes?

00:44:07.069 --> 00:44:08.070 line:90%
[chuckles]

00:44:09.280 --> 00:44:12.450 line:90%
There was this one day
when His Royal Highness

00:44:13.868 --> 00:44:15.995 line:90%
climbed over this wall.

00:44:19.373 --> 00:44:21.500 line:90%
He seemed exceptionally happy that day.

00:44:22.293 --> 00:44:24.879 line:90%
I wondered if he'd hidden
a sweet pot of honey here.

00:44:24.962 --> 00:44:26.881 line:90%
It wasn't until the next day
that I found out

00:44:27.631 --> 00:44:29.175 line:90%
that a maiden was responsible.

00:44:30.509 --> 00:44:31.677 line:90%
[chuckles]

00:44:31.760 --> 00:44:32.887 line:90%
[Lady Choi] And so,

00:44:33.471 --> 00:44:35.055 line:90%
I have faith in the both of you.

00:44:36.056 --> 00:44:39.310 line:90%
You are both desperate
to protect one another, are you not?

00:44:41.437 --> 00:44:42.730 line:90%
[Lady Choi inhales deeply]

00:44:43.772 --> 00:44:45.399 line:90%
The palace gates will be shut soon.

00:44:49.737 --> 00:44:50.738 line:90%
[gasps]

00:44:51.822 --> 00:44:52.948 line:90%
Then can I just…

00:44:53.032 --> 00:44:54.492 line:90%
[♪ upbeat pop music playing]

00:44:54.575 --> 00:44:55.534 line:90%
[breathes heavily]

00:44:55.618 --> 00:44:56.952 line:90%
Oh.

00:44:57.036 --> 00:44:58.621 line:90%
But what if someone asks for me?

00:44:58.704 --> 00:45:00.247 line:90%
Do not worry.

00:45:03.876 --> 00:45:05.878 line:90%
[♪ upbeat pop music continues]

00:45:25.689 --> 00:45:26.690 line:90%
[pants]

00:45:50.339 --> 00:45:51.507 line:90%
[Huiju] <i>I'm sick.</i>

00:45:51.590 --> 00:45:54.093 line:90%
PRINCE

00:45:56.011 --> 00:45:57.012 line:90%
[exhales deeply]

00:46:01.225 --> 00:46:02.226 line:90%
[phone buzzes]

00:46:14.446 --> 00:46:15.864 line:90%
[engine revving]

00:46:26.709 --> 00:46:28.002 line:90%
[footsteps approaching]

00:46:29.128 --> 00:46:30.129 line:90%
[panting]

00:46:31.714 --> 00:46:32.715 line:90%
[♪ music ends]

00:46:32.798 --> 00:46:33.799 line:90%
[pants]

00:46:38.012 --> 00:46:39.013 line:90%
I thought you were sick.

00:46:39.930 --> 00:46:41.098 line:90%
[breathes heavily]

00:46:41.765 --> 00:46:43.350 line:90%
I just wanted to be with you.

00:46:48.272 --> 00:46:49.857 line:90%
I told you I'd be back tomorrow.

00:46:50.482 --> 00:46:51.900 line:90%
[breathing shakily]

00:46:51.984 --> 00:46:52.985 line:90%
Are you okay?

00:47:01.118 --> 00:47:02.911 line:90%
[breathing shakily]

00:47:07.416 --> 00:47:08.542 line:90%
I like you.

00:47:12.004 --> 00:47:13.464 line:90%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:47:32.775 --> 00:47:33.776 line:90%
Stick to one thing.

00:47:35.110 --> 00:47:36.236 line:90%
I'm getting confused.

00:47:38.530 --> 00:47:39.782 line:90%
No, you're not.

00:47:42.701 --> 00:47:43.744 line:90%
You know I like you.

00:47:46.080 --> 00:47:48.374 line:90%
And that I only asked
for a divorce to protect you.

00:47:51.251 --> 00:47:52.586 line:90%
That's why you're mad.

00:48:03.639 --> 00:48:06.642 line:90%
[♪ pop music playing, WOODZ "Everglow"]

00:48:28.831 --> 00:48:29.873 line:90%
You don't want this?

00:48:39.842 --> 00:48:40.843 line:90%
I do.

00:49:28.515 --> 00:49:29.641 line:90%
[objects clatter]

00:49:30.976 --> 00:49:31.810 line:90%
[I-AN chuckles]

00:49:40.486 --> 00:49:41.487 line:90%
[kissing]

00:50:13.727 --> 00:50:14.770 line:90%
[♪ song ends]

00:50:14.853 --> 00:50:16.855 line:90%
[birds chirping]

00:50:24.905 --> 00:50:25.906 line:90%
Your Royal Highness?

00:50:34.498 --> 00:50:35.499 line:90%
You're awake.

00:50:37.000 --> 00:50:38.001 line:90%
What's going on?

00:50:39.253 --> 00:50:40.546 line:90%
[sighs]

00:50:40.629 --> 00:50:41.922 line:90%
I got a call from the palace.

00:50:45.300 --> 00:50:46.301 line:90%
What's wrong?

00:50:47.886 --> 00:50:49.096 line:90%
Did you have a nightmare?

00:50:50.389 --> 00:50:51.390 line:90%
[sighs]

00:50:53.225 --> 00:50:55.102 line:90%
I was just a little scared.

00:51:01.191 --> 00:51:02.568 line:90%
[I-AN sighs]

00:51:03.610 --> 00:51:05.153 line:90%
Stay here for the time being.

00:51:06.822 --> 00:51:09.032 line:90%
By myself? Why?

00:51:09.825 --> 00:51:11.535 line:90%
The second edict will be delivered soon.

00:51:13.078 --> 00:51:14.079 line:90%
And I will

00:51:14.997 --> 00:51:16.164 line:90%
refuse it once more.

00:51:17.499 --> 00:51:18.500 line:90%
Hold on a second.

00:51:20.294 --> 00:51:21.461 line:90%
One step at a time.

00:51:21.545 --> 00:51:24.172 line:90%
Walk me through step by step
so I can understand.

00:51:25.966 --> 00:51:27.259 line:90%
With a royal abdication edict,

00:51:28.760 --> 00:51:30.387 line:90%
it's customary to refuse three times.

00:51:31.847 --> 00:51:33.223 line:90%
And then?

00:51:35.142 --> 00:51:36.184 line:90%
I have to accept it.

00:51:38.812 --> 00:51:41.148 line:90%
But you wanted to protect His Majesty.

00:51:46.236 --> 00:51:47.779 line:90%
I wanted to protect my nephew.

00:51:50.115 --> 00:51:51.116 line:90%
Not the king.

00:51:56.413 --> 00:51:58.540 line:90%
-Whoosh.
-[chuckles]

00:51:58.624 --> 00:52:00.208 line:90%
[I-AN] Whoosh.

00:52:00.292 --> 00:52:03.086 line:90%
[Yun] You intend for Grand Prince I-AN
to ascend the throne?

00:52:04.296 --> 00:52:07.633 line:90%
Have you truly gone mad?
[breathes shakily]

00:52:07.716 --> 00:52:09.968 line:90%
[♪ tense music playing]

00:52:28.528 --> 00:52:29.529 line:90%
[sighs]

00:52:38.622 --> 00:52:39.665 line:90%
What is this?

00:52:40.582 --> 00:52:44.920 line:90%
His Majesty had a garment made for you.

00:52:48.924 --> 00:52:51.426 line:90%
[gasps, breathes shakily]

00:52:56.098 --> 00:52:58.100 line:90%
[♪ tense music intensifies]

00:53:04.898 --> 00:53:05.899 line:90%
[sighs]

00:53:09.194 --> 00:53:10.195 line:90%
It appears my brother…

00:53:12.781 --> 00:53:14.241 line:90%
seeks to abdicate.

00:53:14.783 --> 00:53:16.952 line:90%
But what about the Crown Prince?

00:53:18.954 --> 00:53:20.205 line:90%
[I-AN] <i>I hated him for it.</i>

00:53:21.623 --> 00:53:23.917 line:90%
<i>He turned a blind eye</i>
<i>when I longed for it so desperately.</i>

00:53:25.127 --> 00:53:28.755 line:90%
<i>It felt like he was thrusting the burden</i>
<i>when it was far too late.</i>

00:53:28.839 --> 00:53:30.007 line:90%
[Hyeon] Your Royal Highness!

00:53:30.090 --> 00:53:31.675 line:90%
[footsteps running]

00:53:32.884 --> 00:53:34.261 line:90%
[panting]

00:53:36.221 --> 00:53:37.848 line:90%
Something terrible has happened.

00:53:37.931 --> 00:53:39.182 line:90%
[panting]

00:53:40.434 --> 00:53:41.435 line:90%
[I-AN] <i>But…</i>

00:53:46.481 --> 00:53:47.649 line:90%
<i>I was the one too late.</i>

00:53:49.609 --> 00:53:50.610 line:90%
[♪ music ends]

00:53:54.406 --> 00:53:56.408 line:90%
[♪ mournful music playing]

00:54:00.746 --> 00:54:04.082 line:90%
[I-AN] <i>So I wanted to protect my nephew,</i>
<i>no matter what.</i>

00:54:05.542 --> 00:54:06.585 line:90%
<i>In my brother's place.</i>

00:54:08.295 --> 00:54:09.838 line:90%
Where is the Crown Prince?

00:54:10.380 --> 00:54:11.381 line:90%
[guard] Pardon?

00:54:11.465 --> 00:54:13.091 line:90%
Where is my nephew…

00:54:15.177 --> 00:54:16.553 line:90%
the heir to the throne?

00:54:19.181 --> 00:54:21.183 line:90%
[♪ mournful music continues]

00:54:22.309 --> 00:54:23.310 line:90%
[I-AN] When the Queen Mother

00:54:25.062 --> 00:54:26.980 line:90%
turned a blind eye
to my brother's dying wish…

00:54:33.111 --> 00:54:34.154 line:90%
[breathes shakily]

00:54:34.237 --> 00:54:35.989 line:90%
Even when my nephew told me he was scared…

00:54:40.243 --> 00:54:41.703 line:90%
[breathing shakily]

00:54:42.788 --> 00:54:43.872 line:90%
I hesitated.

00:54:54.257 --> 00:54:55.342 line:90%
If I become king,

00:54:56.843 --> 00:54:58.512 line:90%
I feel like I could protect everyone.

00:55:01.598 --> 00:55:02.599 line:90%
But then again…

00:55:07.437 --> 00:55:08.814 line:90%
I fear it's just my own greed.

00:55:20.867 --> 00:55:21.952 line:90%
You can be greedy.

00:55:28.750 --> 00:55:29.751 line:90%
Let's see this through.

00:55:32.629 --> 00:55:33.797 line:90%
I will be by your side.

00:55:40.595 --> 00:55:42.597 line:90%
[♪ mournful music intensifies]

00:55:51.565 --> 00:55:54.484 line:90%
[protestor on megaphone]
Remove Grand Prince I-AN as regent!

00:55:54.568 --> 00:55:56.611 line:90%
-Remove him!
-Remove him!

00:55:56.695 --> 00:55:59.656 line:90%
[protestor]
Strip Seong Huiju of her rank immediately!

00:55:59.739 --> 00:56:01.741 line:90%
-Immediately!
-Immediately!

00:56:01.825 --> 00:56:05.328 line:90%
[protestor] Grand Prince I-AN and
CEO Seong Huiju must apologize!

00:56:05.412 --> 00:56:07.330 line:90%
[protestors chanting]
Apologize! Apologize!

00:56:07.414 --> 00:56:08.415 line:90%
Your Royal Highness.

00:56:08.498 --> 00:56:10.000 line:90%
[protestors continue chanting
indistinctly]

00:56:10.083 --> 00:56:11.793 line:90%
The Queen Mother is asking for you.

00:56:21.803 --> 00:56:22.804 line:90%
All right.

00:56:35.066 --> 00:56:36.276 line:90%
[sighs]

00:56:36.359 --> 00:56:37.360 line:90%
[door closes]

00:56:50.540 --> 00:56:51.875 line:90%
Tell them you cannot accept.

00:56:55.837 --> 00:56:56.838 line:90%
[sighs]

00:56:57.923 --> 00:56:58.924 line:90%
[scoffs]

00:56:59.758 --> 00:57:01.593 line:90%
Surely you do not intend to accept.

00:57:04.054 --> 00:57:06.723 line:90%
His Majesty has
only eight years of life to his name.

00:57:06.806 --> 00:57:09.017 line:90%
He is incapable
of forming thoughts or intentions!

00:57:09.100 --> 00:57:10.227 line:90%
That is it!

00:57:12.646 --> 00:57:14.272 line:90%
That is exactly the issue.

00:57:15.982 --> 00:57:17.067 line:90%
He has no will

00:57:17.734 --> 00:57:20.362 line:90%
or mind of his own, yet you have him
sit up there as a puppet

00:57:20.445 --> 00:57:21.947 line:90%
tossing him about as you please!

00:57:24.783 --> 00:57:26.201 line:90%
That is precisely the issue.

00:57:28.370 --> 00:57:30.372 line:90%
Is that what you told His Majesty?

00:57:32.123 --> 00:57:35.377 line:90%
You are the one who made
the king into a puppet!

00:57:37.003 --> 00:57:38.004 line:90%
Yes.

00:57:39.422 --> 00:57:40.590 line:90%
I let that happen.

00:57:42.300 --> 00:57:44.886 line:90%
Whether beside or behind him,
he was easily pushed around.

00:57:44.970 --> 00:57:47.264 line:90%
[♪ contemplative music playing]

00:57:47.347 --> 00:57:48.390 line:90%
So now…

00:57:50.725 --> 00:57:52.018 line:90%
I must stand in front of him.

00:57:54.437 --> 00:57:55.814 line:90%
I-AN!

00:57:55.897 --> 00:57:57.774 line:90%
[breathing shakily]

00:58:00.026 --> 00:58:01.027 line:90%
[sighs]

00:58:04.072 --> 00:58:05.073 line:90%
Queen Mother.

00:58:07.242 --> 00:58:09.744 line:90%
You should be thankful
he stepped down on his own.

00:58:11.413 --> 00:58:13.164 line:90%
In consideration of his filial devotion,

00:58:14.708 --> 00:58:15.792 line:90%
I will not ask you…

00:58:17.794 --> 00:58:18.920 line:90%
to pay for your sins.

00:58:23.383 --> 00:58:24.384 line:90%
Why?

00:58:27.304 --> 00:58:30.056 line:90%
Why insist on becoming king only now?

00:58:32.017 --> 00:58:33.560 line:90%
[Yun crying]

00:58:33.643 --> 00:58:35.645 line:90%
[♪ contemplative piano music playing]

00:58:40.692 --> 00:58:42.193 line:90%
I have made my sacrifices.

00:58:44.446 --> 00:58:46.156 line:90%
So you must do the same.

00:58:47.907 --> 00:58:49.993 line:90%
[crying] That is only fair!

00:58:52.912 --> 00:58:53.913 line:90%
[sobbing]

00:59:07.093 --> 00:59:08.553 line:90%
<i>I gave up on my dreams.</i>

00:59:15.101 --> 00:59:17.812 line:90%
You must become the Crown Princess.

00:59:20.023 --> 00:59:21.358 line:90%
[Yun] <i>My future.</i>

00:59:21.858 --> 00:59:23.735 line:90%
[students chattering]

00:59:26.112 --> 00:59:27.280 line:90%
[I-AN] Yun Irang!

00:59:28.740 --> 00:59:30.742 line:90%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:59:44.547 --> 00:59:45.757 line:90%
[chuckles softly]

00:59:49.094 --> 00:59:51.137 line:90%
[Yun crying] <i>And even my heart.</i>

00:59:53.556 --> 00:59:54.557 line:90%
So why?

00:59:55.183 --> 00:59:56.684 line:90%
[breathes shakily]

00:59:56.768 --> 00:59:59.396 line:90%
Why won't you give anything up? [cries]

01:00:06.152 --> 01:00:07.821 line:90%
[sobbing]

01:00:27.298 --> 01:00:28.591 line:90%
[I-AN] Court Lady Im, are you there?

01:00:33.805 --> 01:00:35.140 line:90%
[exhales shakily]

01:00:35.223 --> 01:00:37.142 line:90%
Her Majesty appears weary
in mind and body.

01:00:38.518 --> 01:00:39.602 line:90%
For the next three days,

01:00:41.229 --> 01:00:42.981 line:90%
permit no one to enter her quarters.

01:00:43.773 --> 01:00:45.733 line:90%
[Lady Im] Yes, Your Royal Highness.

01:00:45.817 --> 01:00:47.026 line:90%
[breathes shakily]

01:00:59.205 --> 01:01:01.082 line:90%
-[exhales sharply]
-[Lady Im] Your Majesty…

01:01:05.170 --> 01:01:06.212 line:90%
[sobbing]

01:01:09.424 --> 01:01:10.508 line:90%
[♪ music fades]

01:01:10.592 --> 01:01:12.469 line:90%
[rain pattering]

01:01:12.552 --> 01:01:14.888 line:90%
[Lord INPYEONG on phone]
<i>What on earth are you doing?</i>

01:01:15.472 --> 01:01:17.265 line:90%
<i>If His Majesty refused to open the doors,</i>

01:01:17.348 --> 01:01:19.559 line:90%
<i>you should've torn them down!</i>

01:01:21.436 --> 01:01:23.855 line:90%
[sighs] Never mind.
I will head there now--

01:01:23.938 --> 01:01:25.356 line:90%
[Yun] <i>It will all be in vain.</i>

01:01:26.733 --> 01:01:27.859 line:90%
For the next three days,

01:01:29.569 --> 01:01:32.155 line:90%
no one will be permitted
to enter my quarters.

01:01:32.780 --> 01:01:33.823 line:90%
And why is that?

01:01:35.158 --> 01:01:36.993 line:90%
If the Grand Prince accepts
the abdication,

01:01:37.076 --> 01:01:39.078 line:90%
he will destroy us.

01:01:39.162 --> 01:01:40.163 line:90%
[sighs]

01:01:43.750 --> 01:01:46.127 line:90%
He has stated
he will not hold me accountable.

01:01:46.211 --> 01:01:47.253 line:90%
[Lord INPYEONG] <i>Do you really believe…</i>

01:01:48.671 --> 01:01:50.256 line:90%
[breathing heavily]

01:01:50.340 --> 01:01:54.052 line:90%
Ignoring the late King's dying wish
isn't our only crime.

01:01:54.928 --> 01:01:57.138 line:90%
Even if Prime Minister Min
is covering for us now,

01:01:57.222 --> 01:01:59.557 line:90%
-if he becomes king--
-That is enough!

01:02:00.058 --> 01:02:03.353 line:90%
Do you intend to surrender
all privileges held by the royal family?

01:02:03.436 --> 01:02:04.604 line:90%
Father!

01:02:05.897 --> 01:02:07.732 line:90%
I will take over from here.

01:02:11.236 --> 01:02:12.904 line:90%
What are you plotting now?

01:02:12.987 --> 01:02:15.323 line:90%
It will be too late after his ascension.

01:02:16.658 --> 01:02:18.284 line:90%
What does that mean?

01:02:18.368 --> 01:02:19.869 line:90%
[Lord INPYEONG] <i>Your Majesty,</i>

01:02:20.954 --> 01:02:22.705 line:90%
you just need to protect your quarters.

01:02:22.789 --> 01:02:25.041 line:90%
[♪ suspenseful music playing]

01:02:25.542 --> 01:02:26.543 line:90%
Father?

01:02:27.418 --> 01:02:28.878 line:90%
-[call ends]
-[gasps]

01:02:41.975 --> 01:02:44.435 line:90%
[staff member]
Lord INPYEONG, you have a guest.

01:02:48.773 --> 01:02:51.776 line:90%
[♪ suspenseful music intensifies]

01:03:27.395 --> 01:03:28.688 line:90%
[♪ music fades]

01:03:28.771 --> 01:03:30.565 line:90%
[rain pattering]

01:03:33.818 --> 01:03:35.320 line:90%
[♪ gentle music playing]

01:03:35.403 --> 01:03:38.531 line:90%
-Wow. Is this what he's wearing today?
-Yes.

01:03:39.032 --> 01:03:42.493 line:90%
The last edict will be
personally delivered by His Majesty.

01:03:42.577 --> 01:03:47.123 line:90%
[sucks teeth] But he didn't wear this
to His Majesty's Royal Birthday Banquet?

01:03:47.206 --> 01:03:48.625 line:90%
[gasps] Thank you for bringing that up.

01:03:48.708 --> 01:03:50.918 line:90%
-I went through hell that day--
-[clears throat]

01:03:52.045 --> 01:03:53.880 line:90%
-[chuckles softly]
-[Lady Choi sobbing]

01:03:57.175 --> 01:03:58.176 line:90%
Oh…

01:03:59.636 --> 01:04:01.596 line:90%
His Majesty, the late King,

01:04:02.555 --> 01:04:04.223 line:90%
would have been delighted to see this.

01:04:04.724 --> 01:04:06.142 line:90%
[chuckles, sniffles]

01:04:06.643 --> 01:04:07.644 line:90%
[chuckles softly]

01:04:09.646 --> 01:04:10.730 line:90%
I'm delighted too.

01:04:12.565 --> 01:04:13.691 line:90%
[chuckles]

01:04:14.692 --> 01:04:15.860 line:90%
[Hyejeong] Your Royal Highness.

01:04:19.489 --> 01:04:20.782 line:90%
The Royal Secretariat has notified

01:04:20.865 --> 01:04:22.825 line:90%
the Office of Royal Relatives
and the Prime Minister.

01:04:22.909 --> 01:04:25.745 line:90%
Goodness, they'll all be racing
to the palace now.

01:04:25.828 --> 01:04:26.913 line:90%
[Hyejeong] Before that, we have

01:04:26.996 --> 01:04:29.499 line:90%
some documents from the Secretariat
and Rites for your review.

01:04:30.249 --> 01:04:31.250 line:90%
Are you ready to go?

01:04:33.127 --> 01:04:35.129 line:90%
[♪ hopeful music playing]

01:04:42.303 --> 01:04:43.596 line:90%
I'll be waiting here.

01:04:43.680 --> 01:04:44.681 line:90%
[chuckles softly]

01:04:45.431 --> 01:04:46.432 line:90%
Okay.

01:05:05.660 --> 01:05:06.994 line:90%
[Lady Im] Your Majesty,

01:05:07.078 --> 01:05:08.913 line:90%
His Majesty has arrived.

01:05:08.996 --> 01:05:10.331 line:90%
[door opens]

01:05:17.588 --> 01:05:18.923 line:90%
What brings you here?

01:05:20.717 --> 01:05:21.801 line:90%
Mother.

01:05:21.884 --> 01:05:24.929 line:90%
If you do not intend to rescind it,
you should turn back.

01:05:25.012 --> 01:05:26.431 line:90%
I…

01:05:26.514 --> 01:05:28.349 line:90%
Your father fought to protect that throne!

01:05:30.435 --> 01:05:31.477 line:90%
[His Majesty cries]

01:05:32.937 --> 01:05:37.442 line:90%
Do you have any idea
what he went through to safeguard it?

01:05:37.984 --> 01:05:40.945 line:90%
Do you know what I had to do
to ensure it was passed down to you--

01:05:41.028 --> 01:05:42.697 line:90%
I know!

01:05:43.740 --> 01:05:47.118 line:90%
[sobbing] The day Father passed away…

01:05:48.745 --> 01:05:51.497 line:90%
I heard everything.

01:05:53.624 --> 01:05:54.625 line:90%
-[sobs]
-[gasps]

01:05:57.462 --> 01:06:00.256 line:90%
[♪ mournful music playing]

01:06:02.341 --> 01:06:03.342 line:90%
[gasps]

01:06:03.426 --> 01:06:05.011 line:90%
[His Majesty crying]

01:06:07.346 --> 01:06:08.556 line:90%
How…

01:06:08.639 --> 01:06:10.892 line:90%
[His Majesty crying] <i>I do not want to!</i>

01:06:13.853 --> 01:06:14.896 line:90%
[Yun] Crown Prince!

01:06:15.521 --> 01:06:18.524 line:90%
I do not want to!

01:06:20.234 --> 01:06:21.402 line:90%
[Yun sniffles]

01:06:21.486 --> 01:06:22.987 line:90%
It was your father's dying wish.

01:06:25.239 --> 01:06:26.532 line:90%
[crying]

01:06:27.784 --> 01:06:30.787 line:90%
The only one I can rely on now
is you, Crown Prince…

01:06:33.456 --> 01:06:35.082 line:90%
No. Your Majesty.

01:06:37.210 --> 01:06:38.544 line:90%
[His Majesty crying]

01:06:38.628 --> 01:06:40.505 line:90%
Do not disappoint me.

01:06:52.975 --> 01:06:54.977 line:90%
[breathing shakily]

01:07:06.656 --> 01:07:08.324 line:90%
Mother!

01:07:08.407 --> 01:07:09.826 line:90%
[sobs]

01:07:13.704 --> 01:07:14.747 line:90%
[sobs]

01:07:15.790 --> 01:07:19.377 line:90%
Mother, please forgive me

01:07:20.211 --> 01:07:21.629 line:90%
for disappointing you.

01:07:22.880 --> 01:07:24.257 line:90%
[Yun breathes shakily]

01:07:26.133 --> 01:07:28.135 line:90%
[His Majesty sobbing]

01:07:42.441 --> 01:07:44.443 line:90%
[both crying]

01:07:49.907 --> 01:07:51.909 line:90%
[♪ mournful music continues]

01:07:59.458 --> 01:08:01.460 line:90%
[both sobbing]

01:08:04.881 --> 01:08:06.883 line:90%
[♪ music fades]

01:08:08.217 --> 01:08:09.218 line:90%
Sir.

01:08:09.886 --> 01:08:11.721 line:90%
It's time to head to the Council Hall now.

01:08:13.180 --> 01:08:14.724 line:90%
There's still plenty of time.

01:08:16.809 --> 01:08:17.810 line:90%
[secretary] Yes, sir.

01:08:21.439 --> 01:08:22.899 line:90%
[sighs]

01:08:22.982 --> 01:08:24.984 line:90%
[♪ contemplative music playing]

01:08:27.945 --> 01:08:29.947 line:90%
[birds chirping]

01:08:41.250 --> 01:08:43.586 line:90%
I will take over from here.

01:08:44.629 --> 01:08:45.630 line:90%
[sighs]

01:08:46.839 --> 01:08:49.759 line:90%
[Jeongwoo] <i>You must stop either</i>
<i>the Grand Prince or His Majesty.</i>

01:08:49.842 --> 01:08:51.177 line:90%
Do whatever you must.

01:08:54.180 --> 01:08:55.306 line:90%
[I-AN] <i>I will not ask you</i>

01:08:57.266 --> 01:08:58.392 line:90%
to pay for your sins.

01:08:59.226 --> 01:09:00.227 line:90%
[sighs]

01:09:07.735 --> 01:09:09.236 line:90%
I-AN

01:09:11.364 --> 01:09:12.615 line:90%
[line ringing]

01:09:13.950 --> 01:09:15.326 line:90%
[phone buzzes]

01:09:15.409 --> 01:09:17.662 line:90%
Your Royal Highness,
it is the Queen Mother.

01:09:18.871 --> 01:09:20.039 line:90%
[continues buzzing]

01:09:25.044 --> 01:09:27.421 line:90%
[Jeongwoo] <i>I'd like a brief audience</i>
<i>in the Council Hall.</i>

01:09:28.005 --> 01:09:30.257 line:90%
Do we have time
before we're due at the Throne Hall?

01:09:30.841 --> 01:09:31.717 line:90%
Well…

01:09:32.760 --> 01:09:35.179 line:90%
Yes, we have about 30 minutes.

01:09:35.930 --> 01:09:36.931 line:90%
Right.

01:09:43.562 --> 01:09:44.563 line:90%
[sighs]

01:09:50.611 --> 01:09:52.989 line:90%
[♪ tense music playing]

01:09:53.072 --> 01:09:54.323 line:90%
Court Lady Im.

01:10:00.621 --> 01:10:01.998 line:90%
Yes, Your Majesty.

01:10:05.793 --> 01:10:07.128 line:90%
I need the girl I hid…

01:10:11.424 --> 01:10:12.883 line:90%
brought to the palace.

01:10:16.679 --> 01:10:18.764 line:20%
PROTOCOL FOR THE ACCESSION
OF THE 34TH KING

01:10:18.848 --> 01:10:19.849 line:90%
[sighing]

01:10:21.100 --> 01:10:22.643 line:90%
[sucks teeth] Be honest with me.

01:10:23.310 --> 01:10:24.353 line:90%
About what?

01:10:25.229 --> 01:10:26.355 line:90%
If I become…

01:10:27.481 --> 01:10:29.275 line:90%
If I become the Queen,

01:10:30.526 --> 01:10:32.319 line:90%
people wouldn't like it, right?

01:10:33.612 --> 01:10:35.948 line:90%
Come on now. Your Royal Highness?
Who would ever?

01:10:36.032 --> 01:10:38.367 line:90%
My goodness. Who would dare?

01:10:38.451 --> 01:10:39.452 line:90%
If I ever find them…

01:10:39.535 --> 01:10:41.787 line:90%
Hyejeong would've been
brutally honest with me.

01:10:42.955 --> 01:10:44.957 line:90%
Yes. Well, they won't be too thrilled.

01:10:45.041 --> 01:10:46.292 line:90%
-[chuckles]
-[groans]

01:10:47.626 --> 01:10:49.336 line:90%
Right, exactly!

01:10:49.420 --> 01:10:52.089 line:90%
If I had known about this,
I wouldn't have stepped up.

01:10:52.173 --> 01:10:53.924 line:90%
I was planning
to just take the fall for it

01:10:54.008 --> 01:10:56.552 line:90%
and bounce out of here
without looking back.

01:10:56.635 --> 01:10:58.012 line:90%
No need to get worked up.

01:10:58.554 --> 01:11:03.350 line:90%
Not everyone is a fan
of the Grand Prince, either. [chuckles]

01:11:04.435 --> 01:11:05.895 line:90%
I only have haters.

01:11:05.978 --> 01:11:07.688 line:90%
Oh, I see.

01:11:09.607 --> 01:11:10.608 line:90%
You can do it!

01:11:11.400 --> 01:11:12.610 line:90%
[phone buzzes]

01:11:12.693 --> 01:11:14.904 line:90%
PAIN IN MY ASS

01:11:14.987 --> 01:11:16.530 line:90%
[line ringing]

01:11:18.783 --> 01:11:19.784 line:90%
[Huiju] <i>Yes?</i>

01:11:19.867 --> 01:11:24.413 line:90%
Hey, you said you'd call.
I've been waiting forever, you know.

01:11:24.497 --> 01:11:26.916 line:90%
Should I move to the next step?
Father in the hospital?

01:11:26.999 --> 01:11:29.460 line:90%
No. Don't. Just stop that for now.

01:11:29.543 --> 01:11:32.421 line:90%
Stop? Why? Are they
calling off the company audit?

01:11:33.631 --> 01:11:35.132 line:90%
No, that's not it.

01:11:36.717 --> 01:11:38.844 line:90%
[sighs] Where are you now? Father's place?

01:11:38.928 --> 01:11:41.347 line:90%
-Yeah.
-[Huiju] <i>Stay there. I'll be right over.</i>

01:11:41.430 --> 01:11:42.973 line:90%
-At least tell me what's going…
-[call ends]

01:11:43.057 --> 01:11:44.225 line:90%
Damn brat.

01:11:45.184 --> 01:11:46.977 line:90%
Why? What did Huiju say?

01:11:47.561 --> 01:11:49.480 line:90%
-She's coming here.
-What?

01:11:51.232 --> 01:11:52.233 line:90%
[sucks teeth]

01:12:08.833 --> 01:12:10.835 line:90%
[♪ tense music playing]

01:12:17.591 --> 01:12:19.051 line:90%
[explosion in distance]

01:12:20.636 --> 01:12:22.638 line:90%
[♪ dramatic music playing]

01:12:23.430 --> 01:12:24.431 line:90%
Grand Princess.

01:12:25.057 --> 01:12:26.058 line:90%
You must flee.

01:12:26.142 --> 01:12:27.309 line:90%
[gasps]

01:12:27.393 --> 01:12:30.229 line:90%
Isn't that… the Council Hall?

01:12:33.732 --> 01:12:34.608 line:90%
[explosion]

01:12:37.695 --> 01:12:38.696 line:90%
[breathes shakily]

01:12:50.291 --> 01:12:51.375 line:90%
No…

01:12:51.917 --> 01:12:53.377 line:90%
[breathes shakily] No!

01:12:54.587 --> 01:12:55.588 line:90%
Your Highness!

01:12:57.339 --> 01:12:59.675 line:90%
[clamoring]

01:13:08.225 --> 01:13:09.768 line:90%
[panting, exclaims]

01:13:09.852 --> 01:13:11.979 line:90%
[breathing heavily]

01:13:16.317 --> 01:13:17.318 line:90%
Aide Do.

01:13:17.818 --> 01:13:18.819 line:90%
What…

01:13:21.780 --> 01:13:22.990 line:90%
What are you doing here?

01:13:24.325 --> 01:13:25.784 line:90%
[breathes shakily]

01:13:28.704 --> 01:13:29.705 line:90%
Tell me.

01:13:29.788 --> 01:13:31.290 line:90%
[breathing shakily, whimpers]

01:13:33.042 --> 01:13:34.210 line:90%
Do Hyejeong!

01:13:34.752 --> 01:13:35.753 line:90%
The Council Hall…

01:13:38.756 --> 01:13:39.840 line:90%
His Royal Highness.

01:13:40.883 --> 01:13:42.218 line:90%
He's in the Council Hall.

01:13:42.301 --> 01:13:43.969 line:90%
[breathing shakily]

01:13:47.097 --> 01:13:49.141 line:90%
[♪ dramatic music intensifies]

01:13:55.898 --> 01:13:56.899 line:90%
Your Royal Highness.

01:13:59.485 --> 01:14:00.653 line:90%
[breathes shakily]

01:14:02.613 --> 01:14:03.614 line:90%
Your Royal Highness.

01:14:08.452 --> 01:14:09.453 line:90%
[♪ music fades]

01:14:11.413 --> 01:14:14.333 line:90%
PERFECT CROWN

01:14:14.416 --> 01:14:17.211 line:90%
[| contemplative music playing,
Byeon Wooseok, "Parallel"]

01:14:50.911 --> 01:14:52.496 line:90%
[Hyejeong] <i>His Royal Highness.</i>

01:14:52.579 --> 01:14:53.789 line:90%
<i>He's in the Council Hall.</i>

01:14:53.872 --> 01:14:55.291 line:90%
[Huiju] Your Royal Highness!

01:14:55.374 --> 01:14:57.418 line:90%
Your Royal Highness! [exclaims]

01:14:57.501 --> 01:15:00.462 line:90%
[secretary] <i>There's a rumor circulating</i>
<i>that the Grand Prince has passed away.</i>

01:15:00.546 --> 01:15:01.672 line:90%
What do you mean, regency?

01:15:01.755 --> 01:15:04.091 line:90%
[Jeongwoo] <i>Since the Grand Prince</i>
<i>remains unconscious,</i>

01:15:04.174 --> 01:15:06.760 line:90%
<i>it would only be fitting</i>
<i>for Your Majesty to step forward.</i>

01:15:06.844 --> 01:15:08.220 line:90%
[Hyejeong] <i>The Grand Prince is awake!</i>

01:15:11.598 --> 01:15:14.268 line:20%
[I-AN] <i>I hear rumors of my passing</i>
<i>are spreading outside these walls.</i>

01:15:14.351 --> 01:15:17.271 line:20%
[Huiju] <i>How could one measly royal guard</i>
<i>blow up the Council Hall by himself?</i>

01:15:17.354 --> 01:15:19.106 line:20%
Since the Grand Prince
has regained consciousness,

01:15:19.189 --> 01:15:21.066 line:20%
<i>it's time we tied up some loose ends.</i>

01:15:21.608 --> 01:15:24.153 line:20%
[Huiju] <i>How much do you trust Jeongwoo?</i>

01:15:25.070 --> 01:15:27.781 line:20%
<i>Is there any place safe for you?</i>

01:15:30.659 --> 01:15:32.619 line:20%
Translated by Justin S. Kim

01:15:32.703 --> 01:15:34.663 line:90%
[♪ pop music playing]

01:15:43.922 --> 01:15:47.634 line:90%
PERFECT CROWN